---
// 2. Trust strip - four feature cards.
---
<section class="trust">
  <div class="container trust__inner">
    <div class="trust__card">
      <svg class="trust__icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
      <strong data-i18n="trust.textbook-title">Interactive textbook</strong>
      <span data-i18n="trust.textbook-text">Exam material with translation and audio, in 10 languages</span>
    </div>
    <div class="trust__card">
      <svg class="trust__icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4.5"/><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="4.5"/><line x1="12" y1="19.5" x2="12" y2="22"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="4.5" y2="12"/><line x1="19.5" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/></svg>
      <strong data-i18n="trust.adaptive-title">Smart test picker</strong>
      <span data-i18n="trust.adaptive-text">The app finds what you do not know yet, then shows the fastest way to pass</span>
    </div>
    <div class="trust__card">
      <svg class="trust__icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="23 4 23 10 17 10"/><polyline points="1 20 1 14 7 14"/><path d="M3.51 9a9 9 0 0 1 14.85-3.36L23 10M1 14l4.64 4.36A9 9 0 0 0 20.49 15"/></svg>
      <strong data-i18n="trust.srs-title">Spaced repetition</strong>
      <span data-i18n="trust.srs-text">The app reminds you of words, terms, and questions at the right time, so you do not forget them</span>
    </div>
    <div class="trust__card">
      <svg class="trust__icon" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#34D399" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="19" y1="5" x2="5" y2="19"/><circle cx="6.5" cy="6.5" r="2.5"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="17.5" r="2.5"/></svg>
      <strong data-i18n="trust.math-title">Easy exam math</strong>
      <span data-i18n="trust.math-text">Step by step, with each problem in your language. You do not need to be good at math</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
